3-15T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/174600_439a38b6aaa05a5606fcada064ea0456.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F174600_439a38b6aaa05a5606fcada064ea0456.png&h=59979554&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a9707ceabb9825dfa4d73993618bafad12f42ab","tid":593774,"uid":81282,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"05e778d69ee1fb04eecf092c213d49c247bc7991","tid":593774,"uid":128039,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"係咪打乜都會照寫？<br />\n<br />\n電話響起～<br />\n對方係一位女士：「喂？診所？」<br />\n我：「你好～乜乜診所」<br />\n佢：「幾時截籌呀？」<br />\n我望望鐘：「仲有半個鐘啊」<br />\n佢：「我搭緊的士嚟㗎啦！等埋我呀」<br />\n我：「八點前嚟到就有得睇㗎啦～」<br />\n佢：「我喺的士㗎啦！等埋我呀」<br />\n由於過往好多次經驗，只要你答咗一句『好呀』，之後就會俾人捉住呢句說話嚟炳，所以我哋係唔會再答『好呀』。而會轉為用『八點前嚟到就有得睇』<br />\n<br />\n我：「八點前嚟到就有得睇㗎啦～」<br />\n佢發爛渣：「咁即係等唔等呀？」<br />\n我：「你八點前嚟到就得㗎啦，我哋八點就截症」<br />\n佢：「我知呀，我都話我喺的士度囉！」<br />\n我：「總之你八點前嚟到就OK啦～」<br />\n佢：「我又唔係揸車嗰個，我又唔係架的士！我點知八點前嚟唔嚟到啫！唔通天文台又一定知道聽日好唔好天啦喎，天文台夠成日錯啦！」<br />\n天文台表示躺著也中槍&hellip;<br />\n我：「過咗八點就冇醫生睇㗎啦，醫生會走㗎啦～」<br />\n佢：「你有冇第二句呀？我問你等唔等呀！」<br />\n唔等。<br />\n我：「你過咗八點嘅話，我哋唔會等㗎～」<br />\n佢又發爛渣：「我要生仔嘅你都唔等呀？」<br />\n生仔就去醫院啦，你嚟診所托咩～<br />\n我聽到有把男聲講『師奶你唔係咁搞法呀嘛？你而家生仔呀？喺度呀？』<br />\n佢向男聲講：「揸你嘅車啦！」<br />\n佢再同我講：「嗱，姑娘我同你講呀，香港係有人權㗎，你係冇權拒絕我」<br />\n男聲又出現『你係人，人哋唔L係人呀？你同緊隻狗講電話呀？狗都有狗權呀』<br />\n<br />\n佢向男聲咆哮：「關你咩事呀？我同外星人講電話唔得呀？」<br />\n嘟。我突然被CUT線了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n司機，你安然無恙嗎？<br />\n<br />\n（八點唔見人，收工落閘）<br />\n<br />\n文字來源：診所低能奇觀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/173944_9931e6688f18b78bc97669bf1023b8c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F173944_9931e6688f18b78bc97669bf1023b8c4.jpg&h=00cf06a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/174745_9d25674bbb4f53ff7032e2a6c202a9e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F174745_9d25674bbb4f53ff7032e2a6c202a9e0.png&h=7bfe924f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意你個名多啲"},{"pid":"4d19fe33a4faa018a1e0fa96c119bb4ae2cedc5a","tid":593774,"uid":175088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"My name"},{"pid":"e339178d1e20eecbdbb70f41c2487ae2e84f74c4","tid":593774,"uid":161708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"迪布尼世界第一"},{"pid":"b59cd197219e79037ed5f9b03339f43383ce7526","tid":593774,"uid":81282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c5bb40c03eeff86c055a3bc9de9e8db789fcc6b","tid":593774,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"愛國心是惡黨最後的靠山<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/175058_d7f66e3f855f8c196967891aa2d82bf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F175058_d7f66e3f855f8c196967891aa2d82bf9.png&h=61a4e767&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0daafa0f10480e9c0400a9cc5a35f9e6f8630483","tid":593774,"uid":113234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"我很愉快。。"},{"pid":"07752ec73c009cef4dd3253ac00629d3f32a0ad6","tid":593774,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"70563a9cba28bb3ba91f6bf93f2e23f81645d8d8","tid":593774,"uid":173050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"我個名"},{"pid":"9cf2f597b3d68e86c1c4f2f2ddda6980fe77bf5f","tid":593774,"uid":142508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:52:28.000Z","msg"